song_lyrics: Harakh ati bheṭyā Kṛuṣhṇapati, āj Ekādashī harakh ati... °ṭek
Manmohan māre mandir āvyā, adhik thaī hu to puṇyavatī... āj° 1
Pītāmbar ābhūṣhaṇ paherī, chālantā vahālo hansagati... āj° 2
Puruṣhottam pūraṇ var pāmī, rahī na khāmī have ek rati... āj° 3
Brahmānand kahe Harivar varatā, chaud bhuvanmā hu thaī re chhati... āj° 4
title: Harakh ati bheṭyā Kṛuṣhṇapati
